%pgx
import oracle.pgx.api.*
import oracle.pgx.api.filter.*
import groovy.json.*

baseUrl = 'http://graph-server:7007'
username = 'graph_dev'
password = 'Welcome1'

conn = new URL("$baseUrl/auth/token").openConnection()
conn.setRequestProperty('Content-Type', 'application/json')
token = conn.with {
  doOutput = true
  requestMethod = 'POST'
  outputStream.withWriter { writer ->
    writer << JsonOutput.toJson([username: username, password: password])
  }
  return new JsonSlurper().parseText(content.text).access_token
}

instance = Pgx.getInstance(baseUrl, token)
session = instance.createSession("my-session")
analyst = session.createAnalyst()

%pgx
// Incoming Amount

cs = g.createChangeSet()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT a, SUM(t.amount)
  MATCH (a)<-[t:transfer]-(b)
  GROUP BY a
""")
for (r in rs) {
  v = r.getVertex(1)
  i = r.getLong(2)
  cs.updateVertex(v.getId()).setProperty("in_amount", i)
}
g = cs.build()

g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT ID(a), a.in_amount MATCH (a) WHERE a.type = 'Account'
  ORDER BY a.in_amount DESC
""").print()

%pgx

// Transfer from Victims

cs = g.createChangeSet()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT a, SUM(t.amount)
  MATCH (a)<-[t:transfer]-(v)
  WHERE v.victim = 'true'
  GROUP BY a
""")
for (r in rs) {
  v = r.getVertex(1)
  i = r.getLong(2)
  cs.updateVertex(v.getId()).setProperty("from_victim", i)
}
g = cs.build()

g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT ID(a), a.from_victim MATCH (a) WHERE a.type = 'Account'
  ORDER BY a.from_victim DESC
""").print()

%pgx

// Share Personal Info

cs = g.createChangeSet()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT a1, COUNT(s)
  MATCH (a1)<-[:owns]-(c1)-(s)-(c2)-[:owns]->(a2)
  WHERE a1 != a2 AND c1 != c2
  GROUP BY a1
""")
for (r in rs) {
  a1 = r.getVertex(1)
  share_info = r.getLong(2)
  cs.updateVertex(a1.getId()).setProperty("share_info", share_info)
}
g = cs.build()

g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT ID(a), a.share_info MATCH (a) WHERE a.type = 'Account'
  ORDER BY a.share_info DESC
""").print()

%pgx

// Closeness to Mule Accounts

rs = g.queryPgql("SELECT DISTINCT a MATCH (a) WHERE a.is_mule = 'true'")
vertexSet = g.createVertexSet()
for (r in rs) {
  v = r.getVertex(1)
  vertexSet.addAll(v.getId())
}

analyst.personalizedPagerank(g, vertexSet)

g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT ID(a), a.account_no, a.pagerank, a.is_mule
  MATCH (a) WHERE a.type = 'Account'
  ORDER BY a.pagerank DESC
""").print()

%pgx

g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT
    ID(a)         AS id
  , a.in_amount   AS in_amount
  , a.cashout     AS cashout
  , a.from_victim AS from_victim
  , a.share_info  AS share_info
  , a.community   AS community
  , a.pagerank    AS closeness
  , a.is_mule     AS is_mule
  MATCH (a)
  WHERE a.type = 'Account'
""").print()
